The paper deals with fuzzy automata and their reduction using fuzzy quasi-orders. This topic falls under the sub-category of fuzzy logic (cs.FL) and also involves concepts from mathematical logic (cs.LO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and discrete event systems (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the relationship between fuzzy quasi-orders and determinization of fuzzy recognizers, which is a topic in systems and control theory (cs.SY).
